metadata.name: Lake Ontario
metadata.description:
Took this photo on October of 2022, in Ontario, Canada!

I used a Nikon 300mm f6.3 vintage lens with the Panasonic Lumix G85 to photograph this scene!

"Lake Ontario" by Aymaan Rahman 

I am @aymaanra on Twitter and Instagram
